rue,"","Markdown","Markdown 是一种轻量级标记语言，创始人为约翰·格鲁伯（John Gruber）和亚伦·斯沃茨（Aaron Swartz）。","content/6.maps/_markdown/markdown.md",{"type":183,"children":184,"toc":283},"root",[185,194,200,205,232,237,242,255,260,278],{"type":186,"tag":187,"props":188,"children":190},"element","h4",{"id":189},"markdown-inline-style",[191],{"type":192,"value":193},"text","Markdown Inline Style",{"type":186,"tag":195,"props":196,"children":197},"p",{},[198],{"type":192,"value":199},"通过 VuePress 可以在 Markdown 文件中嵌套 HTML 和 VueJS 代码，然而贴到掘金之后需要我手动贴图，太麻烦了。",{"type":186,"tag":195,"props":201,"children":202},{},[203],{"type":192,"value":204},"于是我测试了几种 Inline CSS 的方案：",{"type":186,"tag":206,"props":207,"children":208},"ul",{},[209,222],{"type":186,"tag":210,"props":211,"children":212},"li",{},[213],{"type":186,"tag":214,"props":215,"children":219},"a",{"href":216,"rel":217},"https://mdnice.com/",[218],"nofollow",[220],{"type":192,"value":221},"MarkdownNice",{"type":186,"tag":210,"props":223,"children":224},{},[225],{"type":186,"tag":214,"props":226,"children":229},{"href":227,"rel":228},"https://github.com/jonkemp/inline-css",[218],[230],{"type":192,"value":231},"InlineCSS",{"type":186,"tag":195,"props":233,"children":234},{},[235],{"type":192,"value":236},"不过结果都不理想，MarkdownNice 的主题，一点儿也不好康。.. InlineCSS 有很多很多很多问题。..",{"type":186,"tag":195,"props":238,"children":239},{},[240],{"type":192,"value":241},"这两种工具我都放弃了，然后我尝试了组合工具的可能性。",{"type":186,"tag":206,"props":243,"children":244},{},[245,250],{"type":186,"tag":210,"props":246,"children":247},{},[248],{"type":192,"value":249},"先通过 SingleFile 将网页保存为一个整体的 HTML 文件",{"type":186,"tag":210,"props":251,"children":252},{},[253],{"type":192,"value":254},"再使用 InlineCSS + Cheerio 手写代码并规避 InlineCSS 的一些配置问题",{"type":186,"tag":195,"props":256,"children":257},{},[258],{"type":192,"value":259},"虽然期间有很多坑，但从最后尝试的结果来说，总的方向可行。",{"type":186,"tag":206,"props":261,"children":262},{},[263,268,273],{"type":186,"tag":210,"props":264,"children":265},{},[266],{"type":192,"value":267},"SingleFile 会自动内联图片和字体文件，这个好解决，处理之前直接打开控制台修改对应元素避免内联即可，比如将图片的 SRC 属性名改为 SRCBACKUP",{"type":186,"tag":210,"props":269,"children":270},{},[271],{"type":192,"value":272},"InlineCSS 合并时 Margin、MarginBottom 这些重复的属性不会被合并，所以出现了部分样式问题",{"type":186,"tag":210,"props":274,"children":275},{},[276],{"type":192,"value":277},"InlineCSS 解析 CSS 不能解析 CSS 变量",{"type":186,"tag":195,"props":279,"children":280},{},[281],{"type":192,"value":282},"因为相关问题很多，虽然方向可行，但还是弃坑了。最近需要贴文章时还是直接贴 Markdown，懒得再做转换了。以后重新再捡起来的时候，也许会写个直接在浏览器中跑的脚本，毕竟直接调用 DOM API 获取样式的稳定性感觉要比用 InlineCSS 好。",{"title":178,"searchDepth":284,"depth":284,"links":285},2,[],"content:6.maps:_markdown:markdown:markdown.md","content","6.maps/_markdown/markdown/markdown.md","6.maps/_markdown/markdown/markdown","md",[292,295],{"_path":293,"title":179,"description":294},"/maps/_markdown/markdown","Markdown 轻量级标记语言学习资源与工具集合",{"_path":296,"title":297,"description":298},"/maps/_medicine/medicine","医疗","常见医疗知识、疾病、药物等。",1772185453954]